  <brief_title>Effect of Long Biliopancreatic Limb RYGB on Weight Loss and Comorbidities</brief_title>
  <acronym>Elegance</acronym>
  <official_title>'Effect of Long biLiopancrEatic Limb lenGth in lAparoscopic Roux-eN-Y Gastric Bypass on Weight Loss and Comorbidities in Patients With Morbid obEsity: a Prospective Randomized Control Trial'</official_title>
